This demo branch shows how the various modules can be combined and used.

----

I use this in my .git/config to work on my private forks of the submodules:

[remote "github"]
	url = git@github.com:DavidS/puppet-manifests.git
	fetch = +refs/heads/*:refs/remotes/github/*
[submodule "modules/common"]
	url = git@github.com:DavidS/puppet-common.git
[submodule "modules/munin"]
	url = git@github.com:DavidS/puppet-munin.git

